sections.heading: Hunting; privately owned land; violations; penalty
sections.text: Any person violating section 37-722 or sections 37-724 to 37-726 shall be guilty of a Class III misdemeanor and shall be fined at least two hundred dollars upon conviction.SourceLaws 1963, c. 199, ยง 5, p. 647;Laws 1977, LB 40, ยง 178;R.S.1943, (1993)
